OL,3,CBBC's Tim Davie backs MasterChef and
OL,4,Csays the show has a 'future beyond
OL,5,C2028'
OL,7,FBBC director-general Tim Davie says he
OL,8,Fbelieves MasterChef does have a future
OL,9,Fwith the broadcaster beyond 2028,
OL,10,Ffollowing the independent report into
OL,11,Fallegations of misconduct against
OL,12,FGregg Wallace.
OL,14,FThe report into Wallace, released on
OL,15,FMonday, found a total of 45 out of the
OL,16,F83 allegations of misconduct made
OL,17,Fduring his time on the show were
OL,18,Fsubstantiated, including one
OL,19,Fallegation of "unwelcome physical
OL,20,Fcontact".
