OL,7,FIt also prompted Wallace's co-
OL,8,FpresenterJohn Torode to confirm he had
OL,9,Fa standalone allegation of racist
OL,10,Flanguage upheld in the same report.
OL,12,FSpeaking as the BBC's annual report
OL,13,Fwas released, Davie said he
OL,14,F"absolutely" thinks the show has a
OL,15,Ffuture.
OL,17,F"It absolutely can survive and
OL,18,Fprosper, but we've got to make sure
OL,19,Fwe're in the right place in terms of
OL,20,Fthe culture of the show," he said.
