OL,7,FThe BBC has been criticised for a
OL,8,Fseries of failings in recent months
OL,9,Fwhich included breaching its own
OL,10,Faccuracy editorial guidelines,
OL,11,Flivestreaming the controversial Bob
OL,12,FVylan set during Glastonbury, and
OL,13,Frecent misconduct allegations
OL,14,Fsurrounding the BBC MasterChef
OL,15,Fpresenter Gregg Wallace.
OL,17,FAddressing the controversy around the
OL,18,FGaza: How To Survive A Warzone
OL,19,Fdocumentary, he said there was "a
OL,20,Fbreach of accuracy" which is "not
OL,21,Facceptable".
